  <description><![CDATA[<p>The sea is the main attraction here with crystal clear water lapping on white sand beaches. The natural landscape has miles of cool pine forests with large areas of Mediterranean maquis stretching down to the sea. Its easy to get away from the crowds and find beautiful little inlets and coves.</p>
<p>Our hotels are near the resort of Villasimius which has a long coastline of incredible soft sand beaches. The capital of <a data-udi="umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9}" title="Sardinia">Sardinia</a>, <em>Cagliari</em>, is nearby and definitely worth a visit if you can tear yourself away from the water's edge.</p>]]></description>
