  <insidersGuide><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">Good to know</p>
<ul>
<li>Head up to the Tower of Chia for amazing views</li>
<li>Hire a car so that you can get to the more remote sights</li>
<li>Take the ferry from Casaletta across to Carloforte to explore the nearby San Pietro Island</li>
</ul>]]></insidersGuide>
